## Defense in Action

Read your assigned case study carefully. Underline or highlight key parts of the story as you go. Then, work together to complete the Defense in Action activity guide.

**Make a copy of the [Defense in Action activity guide](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1mIwIJA8cEIcximlVt56nb5VWN50TF-8Xyt8-jK--TfY/edit?usp=sharing) to get started.**

